  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A hot and cold buffet breakfast is served each day. In the evenings you'll enjoy a four-course dinner with choices and a buffet of starters. Every week the hotel host a gala dinner, which is a great opportunity to taste some local delicacies. On one of your evenings after dinner, you will be treated to a free wine tasting with cheese.</p>
<p>After dinner, head to the sky bar and lounge where you can continue your evening while taking in the panoramic mountain views.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year's Eve gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
